Floppa- If floppa comes into your room just tap his head 4-5 times and he'll leave (you can use the cameras as your petting him!)

Bingus- Just don't look at the same camera he's in and he'll leave you alone

Michael- If he comes into your room just tap his pot and he'll leave

Sogga- If he's asleep then your safe.  However if he is awake then just turn on the music and he'll go back to sleep (don't turn on the music forever that won't work)

Black cat- If he's in cam 3 just stare at him or the alternative solution is to use your camera as little as possible or else he will kill you.  You'll be safe again if you pull down the camera as he's trying to attack.  

Pop Cat- Just double click on the camera that pop cat is in which will play a audio.  The audio will scare away pop cat causing him to retreat.
